{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "bmm-user-creation-v2-2025",
		"name": "Bitcoin Mining Master - 用户创建测试 (2025)",
		"description": "📝 **Bitcoin Mining Master 用户创建 API 完整测试集合**\n\n✅ **功能：**\n- 创建真实用户数据到云端 MySQL 数据库\n- 动态生成唯一 user_id (基于时间戳)\n- 支持完整信息、最小信息、Android 用户等多种场景\n- 自动验证响应状态和数据结构\n\n🔗 **连接架构：**\n```\nPostman → 本地 Node (localhost:8888) → 云端 MySQL (47.79.232.189)\n```\n\n📊 **数据库表：**\n- 数据库：bitcoin_mining_master\n- 表名：user_information\n- 字段：user_id, invitation_code, email, android_id, gaid, register_ip, country, user_creation_time\n\n📅 **创建时间：** 2025-12-04\n\n👤 **使用说明：**\n1. 确保本地 PM2 服务已启动\n2. 选择环境：Bitcoin Mining - Local\n3. 运行推荐测试：\"1️⃣ 创建用户 - 动态时间戳（推荐）\"\n4. 在云端 MySQL 中验证数据",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "1️⃣ 创建用户 - 动态时间戳 (推荐) ⭐",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "prerequest",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"// 生成基于当前时间戳的唯一 user_id",
							"const timestamp = Date.now();",
							"pm.environment.set('timestamp', timestamp);",
							"",
							"// 生成随机邮箱",
							"const randomEmail = `user_${timestamp}@test.com`;",
							"pm.environment.set('randomEmail', randomEmail);",
							"",
							"console.log('🆔 生成的 user_id:', `U${timestamp}`);",
							"console.log('📧 生成的邮箱:', randomEmail);"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				},
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"// 验证响应状态码",
							"pm.test('✅ 状态码为 201 Created', function () {",
							"    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
							"});",
							"",
							"// 验证响应体结构",
							"pm.test('✅ 响应包含 success 字段', function () {",
							"    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('success');",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData.success).to.be.true;",
							"});",
							"",
							"pm.test('✅ 响应包含用户数据', function () {",
							"    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('data');",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('user_id');",
							"});",
							"",
							"// 输出创建的用户信息",
							"const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
							"console.log('✅ 用户创建成功！');",
							"console.log('📊 用户数据:', JSON.stringify(jsonData.data, null, 2));"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json",
						"type": "text"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"user_id\": \"U{{timestamp}}\",\n  \"email\": \"{{randomEmail}}\",\n  \"country\": \"CN\",\n  \"register_ip\": \"192.168.1.100\"\n}",
					"options": {
						"raw": {
							"language": "json"
						}
					}
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/users",
					"host": [
						"{{base_url}}"
					],
					"path": [
						"api",
						"users"
					]
				},
				"description": "**推荐使用！**\n\n✅ 每次运行都会生成唯一的 user_id 和邮箱\n✅ 可以重复运行，不会出现重复错误\n✅ 自动验证响应\n\n**字段说明：**\n- `user_id`: 动态生成 (格式: U + 13位时间戳)\n- `email`: 动态生成 (格式: user_时间戳@test.com)\n- `country`: 中国 (CN)\n- `register_ip`: 测试IP地址"
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "2️⃣ 创建用户 - 完整信息",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "prerequest",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"// 生成唯一标识",
							"const timestamp = Date.now();",
							"pm.environment.set('timestamp', timestamp);",
							"",
							"// 生成邀请码 (13位)",
							"const inviteCode = 'INV' + String(timestamp).slice(-10);",
							"pm.environment.set('inviteCode', inviteCode);",
							"",
							"console.log('🎫 邀请码:', inviteCode);"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				},
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"pm.test('✅ 用户创建成功', function () {",
							"    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
							"    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData.success).to.be.true;",
							"    console.log('✅ 完整信息用户创建成功:', jsonData.data);",
							"});"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"user_id\": \"U{{timestamp}}\",\n  \"invitation_code\": \"{{inviteCode}}\",\n  \"email\": \"fullinfo_{{timestamp}}@example.com\",\n  \"android_id\": \"android_{{timestamp}}\",\n  \"gaid\": \"{{timestamp}}-0000-0000-0000-000000000000\",\n  \"register_ip\": \"203.208.60.1\",\n  \"country\": \"US\"\n}",
					"options": {
						"raw": {
							"language": "json"
						}
					}
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/users",
					"host": [
						"{{base_url}}"
					],
					"path": [
						"api",
						"users"
					]
				},
				"description": "创建包含所有可选字段的用户\n\n**包含字段：**\n- user_id (必填)\n- invitation_code (邀请码)\n- email\n- android_id (Android 设备ID)\n- gaid (Google Advertising ID)\n- register_ip (注册IP)\n- country (国家代码)"
			},
			"response": []
		},
